Author: Brendan Furneaux [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Brendan Furneaux <brendan.furneaux@gmail.com>
Description: Builds in-memory indexes for gzipped FASTA and FASTQ inputs and
    extracts arbitrary subsets of records through an Rcpp backend. Multiple
    files can be indexed as a single logical concatenated source.
